<br>
There *ARE* mobs in other expansions that will summon only off a debuff.  There are not many however.<br>
<br>
This game can be wierd sometimes though.  A few times I would be soloing in 6r with noone else anywhere near the mobs I was fighting. I'd pull an undead mob with slow and I would get summoned instantly.<br>
<br>
I think its possible that if a mob has been damaged before, then it gets the ability to summon people.  Does not  have anything to do with its status of health or anything. <p><img src=http://www.users.qwest.net/~morbid909/ezboardsig.jpg><br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=107355>Those who have turned away, shall be turned upon.</a>
